cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CL

This paper deals with optimization problems in computer vision and machine learning that involve auxiliary latent variables. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of energy-based models, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
